## The Syntax

```dart
// NOT ALLOWED: Standard strings must have data!
String middleName = null; 

// PERFECT: A 'Nullable String' is allowed to be empty.
String? optionalName = null; 
```
By adding the `?`, you've created a **Nullable Type**. It can hold a String, OR it can hold nothing.

